snippet.title: Baldo The Guardian Owls: The Elemental Temples - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Baldo's free update, The Elemental Temples, is available now on PC and consoles. Watch the trailer to see what to expect, including enemies you'll encounter and more in this update, featuring four new dungeons and more. The update is a new standalone adventure for lovers of complex dungeons, and the story follows the events after the Three Fairies DLC and before the Guardian Owls.

#GameTrailers #Gaming #Baldo
